(14, 9, 'Creativity Thinking and Value Innovation', NULL, 'workshop', '2024-08-19', '2024-08-20', 45000, 'NG', '18, Afolabi Aina Street, Allen, Ikeja, Lagos', '50740.pdf', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; color: #c00000;\">Course Overview</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Innovation is essential for staying competitive and achieving long-term success. Our Creativity Thinking and Value Innovation course is meticulously designed to help professionals and organizations improve their creative potential and develop innovative solutions that add significant value. This comprehensive course covers the essential principles of creative thinking and value innovation, providing participants with practical techniques and tools to stimulate creativity and drive innovation within their teams and organizations.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Participants will learn how to generate and evaluate new ideas, transform these ideas into actionable plans, and implement effective innovation strategies. The course delves into various innovation frameworks, such as Blue Ocean Strategy and Design Thinking, and explores how to build a culture of innovation that encourages risk-taking and experimentation. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">By understanding and overcoming common barriers to innovation, participants will be well-equipped to lead and manage innovation initiatives successfully. Through a blend of theoretical knowledge and practical exercises, this course aims to foster an environment where creativity and innovation can thrive, ultimately leading to sustainable business growth and a competitive edge in the market.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; color: #c00000;\">Course Objectives</sp