(15, 9, 'Developing Operational Action Plan MASTERCLASS', NULL, 'workshop', '2024-09-23', '2024-09-25', 80000, 'NG', '18, Afolabi Aina Street, Allen, Ikeja, Lagos', '76918.pdf', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin; color: #c00000;\">PROGRAM OVERVIEW</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">This program will provide you with the skills to develop an operational plan, acquire resources, monitor progress and evaluate performance. You\'ll explore options and contingencies in operational planning, and walk away armed with skills that help you minimize risk and deliver results for your organization.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">The aim of this course is to help managers to, through a process of on the job, action-based thinking-doing, learning-adapting cycles, grounded in the reality of the current organizational strategy and business environment, to take ownership of the planning and implementation cycle.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Value is created by empowering key staff with a proven set of principles, tools and techniques to turn the strategy into effective operational actions. The methodology will include analysis of the strategy; identifying critical factors for individuals, teams and departments in implementing the strategy effectively, provide a framework for robust decision-making required to implement the strategy and create organizational alignment behind achieving the goals and objectives of the strategy.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Is this course right for you?</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">If you\'re a manager with any form of responsibility for planning and monitoring work at an operational level in your organization, this is an essential course for you and your career.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin; color: #c00000;\">Learning Outcomes</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Upon completion of this course you&rsquo;ll be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&sect;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Develop activities based operational plan aligned with the organisation strategic intent</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&sect;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Develop key performance indicators (KPIs) and collate, analyse and organise details of the resources needed to achieve them, including recruitment of staff</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [