107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Developing and recording operational strategies for achieving the purpose of a unit.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Aligning the operational strategy of a unit with the overall strategy of an entity.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Following a systematic process to develop goals, objectives and performance standards that are clear, concise, measurable and achievable.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-ascii-f